## Shop and gold system

- **Currency**: Gold only. Earned via daily login, challenges, minigame wins. Persist in Supabase `user_data` (gold, total_gold_earned, shop_owned).
- **Challenges**: `lib/shopData.js` CHALLENGES; award via `awardChallenge(conditionKey)` (repeatable vs one-time). Variable amounts via `awardGold(amount)` in minigames.
- **New shop items**: Add to SHOP_ITEM_POOL; for fonts add to PROFILE_FONT_FAMILY_MAP (`app/profile.jsx`) and SHOP_FONT_FAMILY_MAP (`app/shop.jsx`).

---

## Conventions

- **React**: Functional components, hooks; import `useCallback` when used.
- **Supabase**: Lazy-load or require in try/catch; app must run without config.
- **No API routes**: Do not add API routes or external data APIs unless the user explicitly asks.
- **Scripts**: `package.json` (start, android, ios, web, verify-icons, check-env, import-wallpapers); `scripts/` or `.scripts/` or root for ad-hoc scripts. Env: ENV_SETUP.md, check-env. SQL: `supabase/` folder.

---

## Main prompt (bundle)

When implementing anything: (1) Read this rule file and **`GOALS.md`**; apply them. (2) Update the correct part of the app (builds, stats, skins, database, patch hub, tier list, custom build, my builds, more, shop, profile, wordle, ability, menu). (3) If the user mentions menu or navigation, update `app/index.jsx` nav/sub-nav. (4) Keep shop and profile in sync with Supabase; show gold where relevant; use `lib` helpers for gold; keep non-routes out of `app/`; maintain Supabase fallbacks. (5) After completing work, update **`GOALS.md`** (check off done items; "Recent progress" = major items only, minor bugs = one short line). If you added new features or conventions, update this rule file too so the agent never forgets.
